snippet.title: TrashPatrol - GamePlay Trailer
snippet.description:
Trash Patrol is a Local Co-op Multiplayer game for 2-4 players. 
Play as a team of Raccoons with your friends and steal items from the humans' house!

Wash and dry the items before throwing them into the teleporting trashcan with a black hole, evade or distract the human and create some chaos!

Download Trash Patrol now on 
Itch.io: https://thetrashcangang.itch.io/trash-patrol
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1969130/Trash_Patrol__Academic_Version/
